latestIgtvVideos.caption:
featuring my oldie :- 

while on my regular feeding routine ,I hear a dog wining in a feeble and shaky voice 
I follow the voice ,saw a petrified old dog surrounded by a bunch of young dog who are trying to bully him 
oldie have no stength to fight with them he is just trying to secrete himself  and sitting down the car 

I call him out at first he was unsure then he came out with hope that I have some food in hand he started pouncing that's when his real personality came out 
He is  still a "puppy by heart "
 He ate his food I watch him loveingly ,satisfying my soul ,promising him that I will come daily to feed him ,his eyes were hopeful  and we bid a goodbye 
  To meet again 

That 's how we met and still meeting daily at the same sunrise ,same place ,with same trust and love 

A lot more sunrise to see ,a lot more goodbyes to meet again are  yet to come !

latestPosts.caption:
From surviving Rugged Streets life to Snow flakes, Road trips and Cuddles. 🇮🇳🇺🇲
Maple found her forever family Seven seas Apart🏡🧿
Maple was rescued off the streets when she was mercilessly mauled by a pack of dogs leaving her with multiple wounds and a leg bone peeping out of her skin at the age of barely 1 month old.
Even After Going Through The Worst 
Nothing Could Take Over Her Friendly deveneour And Cheerful Personality...
Maple has survived against all odds! 
While people in India care more about her being an indie dog and a female and not about the fact that how resilient and loving she is ... Even after multiple adoption appeals Maple was denied a forever loving home in India. She has waited for over a year to get the love of her forever family.

On April 11th 2024 Maple travelled Seven oceans apart from Delhi to Dallas, while her forever' family waited to pick her up from the airport along with her loving and gentle canine brother benny and go on an 18 hour road trip to their home in Denver.
After a long wait maple got the absolute best and It's indeed a fairytale maple found the loveliest family, a Pawfect match that was destined to be.

All the uncertainties are things of the Past Now life is all about zoomies, cuddles and toy treasure hunts along with canine brother Benny.
Ashita and Adam were quite adamant to adopt maple and make her the part of their furry family.
Not just waiting extremely patiently but also sticking by through thousand changes in plan as moving a dog seven ocean apart is not a cake walk.
My heart goes merrier whenever I hear an update about Maple from her benevolent family knowing how much they adore her. 
Seeing her photos embarking on different
adventures or sleeping on a comfy couch beside his loving family. Now Her life is overflowing with tenderness and warmth.
Thank you to all the people who have been a part of maple's journey to her loving family.
My Baby is Home Finallyy 💖

Meandmy_pooches Needs Your Help!
Really grateful towards reaching 14% But there is a long way to Go..

In the Last two months I have rescued many dogs and few of them are going to live permanently in paid boarding as one is paralysed and the other one is a tripod post amputation surgery, for the third one things are still unsure as he is taking slow steps towards recovery.

Even after constant appeals I was not able to find a monthly boarding sponsor for 4 of My Rescues who were shifted in the boarding in the month of January & February respectively.
 Apart from boarding expenses, medical expenses, veterinary bills and monthly food expenses for our 100+ dogs living on the streets of North Delhi that we feed daily.

I am so grateful for the people who have supported my little charity, I need your help once again.

If you will go through the fundraiser I have explained everything and added all the veterinary bills and boarding bills etc. 

The fundraiser aims to raise enough funds to continue to pay for my rescue boarding and medical expenses as well as medications required as two of them are a victim of a terrible accident and need medical attention. 
The fundraiser also aims to Raise for monthly food expenses of 100+ dogs that we feed daily living on the streets of North delhi and take care of their medical needs as well. 

Instagram reach has gone down significantly and not letting us reach even 10 % of our followers and we are struggling to raise funds. 

Now the only hope lies with your shares if you could share the fundraiser/ Create supporting fundraiser and help me reach more people. So that meandmy_pooches could sustain and continue to save more lives.

I had the absolute privilege to foster this beautiful boy for a few days. But he is looking for a forever home. 

Noddy is 3, vaccinated and neutered. He has a slight twitch (adorable) around his ears from the distemper but he is otherwise healthy now. He is house trained and is learning how to walk on leash without pulling much and slowly learning to control distractions. He is highly food motivated and will therefore be a good learner once he settles into a routine. He is open to pan-India adoptions. Please share and feel free to reach out to me if you think you can open your home and your heart for this beautiful baby boy.

Rescue Story:-
Meet the Six puppies Rescued from a Sewage Drain where they would have died by drowning in overflowing Filthy Rain water. They are barely 25 days old right now Rescued from a hell hole. 

While we managed to save 6 puppies sadly one of the puppy died by drowning. 
Their life in the drain was only Subjected to Darkness, filthy water, garbage & Cruel Death. We have miserably failed in every single plan to settle them outside the drainage sewage. Now their fate is either  warmth & love in forever home or a suffocating cruel death back inside the filthy drain 😢

Female:- Mishti, Chikki & jalebi 
Male:- Barfi, Kaju, Ladoo

Bring ths savour of Sweetness your home🥺

Please come forward to foster/Adopt them and save them from a life inside Sewage Drain!
They are available for Foster/Adoption as individually or in Pairs. 

They have been regularly dewormed as per their age. 
 
📍Location:- Delhi / NCR but Open for pan India adoption ( adopter have to pitch in for half the travel cost).

Feed a hungry stray today🐶

We feed over 100+ dogs on the streets of North Delhi mainly around the slum areas and unorganised colonies Inhabited around public parks nearby.
We provide the only source of food available to these dogs to fill their empty bellies. Each one of them eagerly wait for their wholesome meal
But we can't do this alone and need your help to continue to feed our dogs every single day.

It's been really difficult lately to raise required funds to continue to feed our community dogs 

It costs 400 INR or 6 USD  to feed a dog for an entire month, A cost of coffee or a pizza for a day can Fill a stray dog's belly for an entire month.

Or You can also Sponsor a Day feeding for 100+ stray dogs at 1200 INR 

If you wish to Donate in Kind you can Order dog food bags directly via Amazon Wishlist (link in bio)...

latestPosts.caption:
BELLA NEEDS YOUR HELP!

A moment of fun made Bella suffer from unimaginable pain for weeks.
Steel wire traps are illegal and inhumane. Young BELLA has been suffering for weeks while her trauma went unnoticed. Poor girl is the sweetest dog you'll meet. trusting of humans - Even after the trauma she has been through by human hands..
The wire was so tightly wrapped around her paw it slowly cut off all blood circulation till the flesh turned necrotic and died. I cannot imagine her pain and suffering she sustained for so long and now She is on the verge of losing her one leg and living a new life as a tripod(three legged dog).

Please help me raise the remaining Rs.10,000 ($120) towards her initial medical fundraiser to help save her life and cover her ongoing medical expenses towards her leg Amputation surgery, Boarding expenses, Treatment, blood test, transportation & miscellaneous medication.

I'm also looking for a kind virtual parent for Bella towards her boarding expenses that is going to be Rs.10,000 ($120) per month.
Someone who could commit to fully/Partially sponsor her boarding expenses for any given amount every month till she gets Adopted and finds a loving home.
A virtual parent gets regular updates of the dog and can go and meet their virtually adopted dog at the boarding. 

If we couldn't find a virtual parent/ boarding Cost sponsors. we unfortunately have to release tripod Bella back after her recovery to the heavy traffic lane right next to a metro station from where she was rescued. As a tripod dog it's going to be very difficult for her to manage living back on the roads!

Let's give her a second chance. Humans did this to her but humans only can help her too. Let's be good for her. Let her live again. 

To Donate:- 
Gpay/Paytm at 9891071081
QR is attached in 5th slide
**Paypal link and millap fundraiser link is in bio***

Please DM In case you need more Details or need more information/ Any questions regarding being her virtual parent 🙏🏻

latestPosts.caption:
Molly's Eyes are full of hope looking for a forever family who will promise to not abandon her like the people whom she considered as her family did previously...

I Rescued Molly off the streets when she was mercilessly abandoned all alone tied to a pole with her litter of puppies. While 2 of the puppies died in the next few days. Molly was rescued off the streets with one of her puppy who got adopted & now named Honey but molly continues to wait!

Molly's past has been unfortunate but we can make sure her future is full of love & care.

Molly is currently living at a boarding In Noida and she quickly gets along with the boarding staff and continues to be comfortable in their presence..

Molly
Female
German shepherd Mix
To be Spayed Soon
Vaccination up to date 

We are urgently looking for an experienced family who could foster/ foster to Adopt Molly within Delhi NCR

If you wish to make molly a part of Your life Please DM @meandmy_pooches or WhatsApp at 9891071081

We really hope someone comes Forward for Molly 
💟
